1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,182
=Episode 14=

12
00:00:47,540 --> 00:00:48,899
Your Majesty, the fake

13
00:00:48,900 --> 00:00:50,979
(Shangguan Qing)
Yanbo Parlor is nearly finished.

14
00:00:50,980 --> 00:00:52,539
Famed court performers and folk artists

15
00:00:52,540 --> 00:00:54,899
from across the realm
have all taken residence there.

16
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:56,739
We await only
Your Majesty's honoured visit.

17
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:57,699
Excellent.

18
00:00:57,700 --> 00:00:59,899
That is truly joyous news.

19
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:03,299
All my ministers
shall attend my Yanbo Parlor

20
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:04,900
and partake in the festivities.

21
00:01:05,020 --> 00:01:06,580
Shangguan Qing, how dare you.

22
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:08,299
Do you not realise this court

23
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:11,380
is where state affairs are deliberated?

24
00:01:11,580 --> 00:01:12,699
And yet you bring

25
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:14,779
such entertainers into court.

26
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:15,939
This is outrageous!

27
00:01:15,940 --> 00:01:18,299
Minister He,
do not fault Shangguan Qing.

28
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:19,899
This was my doing.

29
00:01:19,900 --> 00:01:20,699
I...

30
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:22,379
also wished my ministers to see

31
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:23,739
where the treasury silver

32
00:01:23,740 --> 00:01:25,579
has been spent.

33
00:01:25,580 --> 00:01:27,980
I want you all to relax a little

34
00:01:28,060 --> 00:01:30,860
and judge whether it was worth it.

35
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:32,180
Shangguan Qing.

36
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:34,580
Yes, Your Majesty.

37
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:40,500
Rise.

38
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:33,300
Splendid!

39
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:40,900
General Xiang Gu
returns victorious to court.

40
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:57,100
(General Xiang Gu)
Xiang Gu, at your service.

41
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,620
Welcome back, General Xiang.

42
00:02:59,820 --> 00:03:00,940
Perfect timing.

43
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:03,139
I've arranged a new dance today.

44
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:04,900
Come and enjoy it with us.

45
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:09,980
Your Majesty,

46
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:11,419
General Xiang

47
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:13,499
has campaigned
in the Southern Seas for years

48
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:14,939
and commands great prestige.

49
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:16,379
Now that unrest stirs at the frontier,

50
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:19,259
it would be fitting
to have him lead the expedition

51
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:20,820
to subdue the barbarians.

52
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:22,379
(So the force)

53
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:25,380
(blocking my contact
with the foreign powers...)

54
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:27,540
(was them all along?)

55
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:30,099
Minister He,

56
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:31,939
General Xiang is advanced in years.

57
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:33,099
He has just returned,

58
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:35,140
and has yet
to enjoy time with his family.

59
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:36,899
How can you still urge His Majesty

60
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,779
to send him back to war?

61
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:39,899
In my view,

62
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:43,259
Your Majesty should instead
grant him further honours and rank,

63
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:44,579
so that he may

64
00:03:44,580 --> 00:03:47,540
remain in the capital
and enjoy family life.

65
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:50,339
Minister Sun, that is mistaken.

66
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:52,819
Soldiers at the frontier
exist to serve the realm.

67
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:55,420
Even death
on the battlefield is no cause for fear.

68
00:03:56,420 --> 00:03:57,379
Your Majesty,

69
00:03:57,380 --> 00:03:59,299
I am willing to lead the campaign

70
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,699
and pacify the frontier.

71
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,699
Good.

72
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,699
Great Qian

73
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:04,699
needs loyal generals like you

74
00:04:04,700 --> 00:04:06,380
true pillars of the realm.

75
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,980
General Xiang,

76
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:12,060
you haven't returned home in ten years.

77
00:04:12,140 --> 00:04:14,180
Do you not wish to go back?

78
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:17,019
Director Jia

79
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:20,140
and Minister Sun are
behaving rather strangely.

80
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:21,779
No need to increase military spending,

81
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:24,580
and yet frontier forces
would still be reinforced.

82
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:25,939
But the two of you

83
00:04:25,940 --> 00:04:28,300
seem oddly reluctant.

84
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:29,780
Could it be

85
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:32,700
you have other thoughts?

86
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,139
We wouldn't dare.

87
00:04:35,140 --> 00:04:36,659
Minister He, you misunderstood.

88
00:04:36,660 --> 00:04:37,779
I am only concerned

89
00:04:37,780 --> 00:04:41,180
for General Xiang's health.

90
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,740
Your Majesty,

91
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:47,459
as the old saying goes,

92
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:50,299
a gentleman settles his household
before serving his cause.

93
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:53,339
General Xiang's granddaughter
has now come of age

94
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,859
and awaits marriage.

95
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:55,859
And Your Majesty happens

96
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:58,820
to lack an empress.

97
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:12,460
Minister He is right.

98
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:15,660
But with the frontier unsettled,

99
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:18,419
I have no mind to take a wife.

100
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:19,619
Your Majesty,

101
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:22,099
you have governed
in your own right for over half a year,

102
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:24,699
yet the harem remains empty.

103
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,980
That is a grave matter
for the royal bloodline.

104
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:30,179
If Your Majesty is
unwilling to appoint an empress,

105
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:32,099
then perhaps you could
announce the identity

106
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:34,419
of the woman you once mentioned.

107
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:36,219
The Ministry of Rites can
make the arrangements.

108
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:39,540
Elevating her as a consort
would not be improper.

109
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,979
This again.

110
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:42,259
I've already said

111
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:44,220
the time isn't right.

112
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:46,220
Besides...

113
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:49,140
a woman such as her

114
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:52,540
could only ever be my empress.

115
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:54,099
Your Majesty,

116
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:55,939
what could be the reason?

117
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:58,179
Rumours are already
spreading among the people.

118
00:05:58,180 --> 00:06:01,099
You must consider
the dignity of the royal family.

119
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,259
What rumours?

120
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:03,219
Well...

121
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:06,460
It's...

122
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:09,899
They involve
Your Majesty and a eunuch.

123
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:11,379
The words are too disgraceful.

124
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:14,939
I cannot bring myself to say them.

125
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:17,859
I beg Your Majesty to take consorts
and appoint an empress,

126
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:21,220
so that Great Qian's lineage
may continue.

127
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:23,019
Minister He,

128
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:24,260
please rise.

129
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:26,859
We beg Your Majesty to
take consorts and appoint an Empress,

130
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:29,180
for the continuation
of Great Qian's royal bloodline.

131
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:31,459
Your Majesty, reconsider.

132
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:33,339
For the sake of succession.

133
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:35,019
Your Majesty, reconsider.

134
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,980
For the sake of succession.

135
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:55,659
I can't hear you.

136
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:57,180
Louder.

137
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,979
Your Majesty, reconsider.

138
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:00,900
For the sake of succession.

139
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:02,180
Louder.

140
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:04,139
Your Majesty, reconsider.

141
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,860
For the sake of succession.

142
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:17,019
Louder.

143
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:18,459
Your Majesty, reconsider.

144
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:20,140
For the sake of succession.

145
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:24,979
Louder still.

146
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:26,539
Your Majesty, reconsider.

147
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:28,340
For the sake of succession.

148
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,339
Louder. I said louder.

149
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:35,779
Your Majesty, reconsider.

150
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:37,420
For the sake of succession.

151
00:07:41,740 --> 00:07:42,659
Louder.

152
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:44,339
Your Majesty, reconsider.

153
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:46,220
For the sake of succession.

154
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:49,380
Enough.

155
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,820
I've had my fill of dancing today.

156
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:53,739
If this matter is raised again,

157
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:55,940
I'll have all of you dance with me.

158
00:07:56,140 --> 00:07:57,419
My marriage

159
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:58,820
is mine to decide.

160
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:01,060
No one is to interfere.

161
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:02,420
Court dismissed.

162
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:14,059
Your Majesty was rather impulsive

163
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:16,300
in court today.

164
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:18,620
If they keep pressing me,

165
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:20,860
I'll deal with them the same way.

166
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:24,300
They say serving
an emperor is like serving a tiger.

167
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:26,339
But with our young emperor,

168
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:29,180
it's like serving a dance partner.

169
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:31,739
They say a tiger's tail
must never be touched.

170
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:33,820
But our young emperor's tail

171
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:35,099
is

172
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,220
love.

173
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:39,059
Aunt, please don't tease me.

174
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:41,340
I think you did the right thing.

175
00:08:41,460 --> 00:08:43,939
The Chu bloodline has
always been passionate.

176
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:47,420
We value love as much as the realm.

177
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:51,820
Let's discuss serious matters.

178
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:54,300
Serious matters?

179
00:08:57,460 --> 00:08:58,299
Duan Muzhi.

180
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,139
Yes.

181
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:01,059
Have the men
sent to investigate Sun Gong

182
00:09:01,060 --> 00:09:02,660
reported back?

183
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:03,939
Your Highness,

184
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:05,339
nothing suspicious has been found

185
00:09:05,340 --> 00:09:06,980
about his background.

186
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,820
You and Uncle have
shared a loving marriage for years.

187
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,660
What is sincere and what is false

188
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,820
can't possibly

189
00:09:16,980 --> 00:09:19,020
escape your perceptive eyes.

190
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:22,700
Speaking of perceptiveness,

191
00:09:23,660 --> 00:09:24,459
I fear

192
00:09:24,460 --> 00:09:26,460
I'm no match for you, Your Majesty.

193
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:29,619
Ever since I learned dancing from you,

194
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:31,459
I haven't been
able to stop for a moment.

195
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:32,419
Had I known,

196
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:33,739
I should have joined

197
00:09:33,740 --> 00:09:35,580
His Majesty in dancing at court.

198
00:09:40,220 --> 00:09:41,340
Serious matters.

199
00:09:41,380 --> 00:09:42,500
Serious matters.

200
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:45,300
Alright.

201
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,659
As for General Xiang,

202
00:09:48,660 --> 00:09:52,179
he is a man of the battlefield, but his loyalty
to the royal family is unquestionable.

203
00:09:52,180 --> 00:09:54,180
He was trusted by my brother.

204
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:56,659
When the Zhen clan was
condemned for treason,

205
00:09:56,660 --> 00:09:57,699
he carried out the decree

206
00:09:57,700 --> 00:09:59,660
without hesitation.

207
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:01,339
He led the troops

208
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:02,540
to execute them.

209
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:08,540
I know you wish to investigate
the Xiao family case.

210
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:10,260
So do I.

211
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:13,020
But now is not the time.

212
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:16,499
Our priority is to use Xiang Gu

213
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,860
to check Jia Yi's armed ambitions.

214
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:23,620
And prevent
the capital's calamity from years ago.

215
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,100
General Xiang,

216
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:37,820
take a look.

217
00:10:38,940 --> 00:10:40,300
Every year,

218
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,939
Jia Yi finds high-sounding excuses

219
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:43,299
to divert military funds.

220
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:47,100
This year, he even urged His Majesty
to build a replica Yanbo Parlor,

221
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:49,179
and recruited famed
performers into the palace.

222
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:52,260
If enemies were to strike one day,

223
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:54,380
what would become of us then?

224
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:58,260
That cursed Sun Gong

225
00:10:58,340 --> 00:11:00,099
has likely taken Jia Yi's favors,

226
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:01,660
and turned a blind eye.

227
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:02,820
However,

228
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:05,220
with the Grand Princess
overseeing things,

229
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:07,099
Sun Gong appears clean-handed,

230
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:09,620
with nothing suspicious for now.

231
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:11,580
But there is one matter.

232
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:14,219
Doesn't it strike you

233
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:16,660
that the eunuch
serving His Majesty called Xiao Man

234
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:18,780
looks rather familiar?

235
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:21,260
He resembles someone from the past.

236
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:23,580
A mere eunuch.

237
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:25,140
I barely noticed him.

238
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,780
Who does he resemble?

239
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:34,260
Xiao Congrong.

240
00:11:58,300 --> 00:11:59,660
General Xiang,

241
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:01,700
your returned at the right time.

242
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,299
We should act at once,

243
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:06,259
and join the court
in curbing the eunuchs' power

244
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:08,940
to stop Jia Yi's excesses.

245
00:12:19,020 --> 00:12:21,220
Curb my power?

246
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:25,979
You think to obstruct
our dealings with foreign powers

247
00:12:25,980 --> 00:12:29,140
and our plan
to overthrow the Chu regime?

248
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:30,740
Wishful thinking.

249
00:12:31,620 --> 00:12:33,259
We must move faster

250
00:12:33,260 --> 00:12:34,780
and finish this soon.

251
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:35,779
Uncle.

252
00:12:35,780 --> 00:12:36,659
Brother.

253
00:12:36,660 --> 00:12:37,419
If all our actions

254
00:12:37,420 --> 00:12:39,259
only clear Father and Mother's names,

255
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:40,299
what then?

256
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:42,860
Must we drag so many others into this?

257
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:45,860
Many veteran officials were involved.

258
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,539
Are you certain His Majesty can shake

259
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:48,859
their hold over the court

260
00:12:48,860 --> 00:12:50,340
and clear your name?

261
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:52,340
Sister,

262
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:53,739
do not speak of

263
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:55,700
clearing names again.

264
00:12:56,420 --> 00:12:58,899
Such things mean nothing to the dead.

265
00:12:58,900 --> 00:13:00,380
Brother,

266
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,539
if we follow Uncle's plan,

267
00:13:02,540 --> 00:13:04,779
countless innocent people will die.

268
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:06,060
Zhen Mujun!

269
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:11,819
Your father and mother

270
00:13:11,820 --> 00:13:14,419
gave their lives
in service to Great Qian.

271
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:16,220
And what did they receive in return?

272
00:13:16,340 --> 00:13:18,619
Because of that tyrant's suspicion,

273
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:21,419
one hundred and eight lives
of the Xiao family

274
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:23,300
were all cut down.

275
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:24,619
Tell me,

276
00:13:24,620 --> 00:13:25,980
if the case were overturned,

277
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,659
would my brother and his wife,

278
00:13:27,660 --> 00:13:28,699
your parents,

279
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:31,380
and your family come back to life?

280
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:33,699
Why should that tyrant
decide who lives or dies,

281
00:13:33,700 --> 00:13:35,420
and when he regrets it,

282
00:13:35,460 --> 00:13:37,900
he can simply brush it aside?

283
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:42,260
I will never accept such an outcome.

284
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:44,620
And neither should you.

285
00:13:50,540 --> 00:13:51,660
Xiao Man,

286
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:55,780
my heart aches.

287
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:58,819
As though there is a wound

288
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,540
that never stops festering.

289
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:04,620
I've endured
this pain for twenty years,

290
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:07,220
twenty long years.

291
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:10,980
I can bear it no longer.

292
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:13,860
Clearing names

293
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:18,060
won't bring the dead back.

294
00:14:19,700 --> 00:14:21,140
What I want

295
00:14:22,100 --> 00:14:25,980
is the old emperor's
bloodline and his throne.

296
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:28,700
I want him to pay
for the lives he murdered!

297
00:14:49,712 --> 00:14:53,632
♪I wanted to ask you
the meaning of forever♪

298
00:14:54,037 --> 00:14:57,157
♪Is it longing that never rests♪

299
00:14:57,812 --> 00:15:01,069
♪Love that echoes without end♪

300
00:15:02,362 --> 00:15:05,957
♪Or promises that can't be kept♪

301
00:15:07,912 --> 00:15:11,332
♪All those vows of forever we made♪

302
00:15:11,874 --> 00:15:15,319
♪Are sealed away in darkness now♪

303
00:15:17,112 --> 00:15:19,919
♪How cruel♪

304
00:15:20,037 --> 00:15:24,194
♪Love blooms and withers♪
